title: Elvis Presley - The Essential 60's Masters 5-CD Set [FLAC+MP3]
description:
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Elvis Presley - From Nashville to Memphis: The Essential 60's Masters

Source: 5-CD Box Set With 2 Fresh Cover Art Scans
---------------------------------------------------------------------

Normally Big Papi does not make FLAC from oldies but this 5-CD set has been digitally remastered except for a couple of tracks that retain the original master recording. Those tracks are annotated in the song titles.

Tags have been edited so this compilation will show up as 1 Album with 5 CD's inside. The default view from the factory is 5 Albums. If you want the 5 Album view (because each Disc has its own cover art, for example) then select all the tracks in each CD and add "Disc 1" "Disc 2" etc to the ALBUM name field.

I hope you enjoy this wonderful collection and do make some copies for family and friends. Thank you for the generous seeding. When some new pirate wants this a year from now you are the ones making that happen.

- Big Papi
